<div class="row applications">

   <div class="nine columns">

        <h2>Applications</h2>

        <p><strong>Apply now for <%= workshop.title %></strong>! <%= workshop.applications.geography %> </p>

        <p>Applications are <strong>due <%= workshop.applications.deadline %></strong>, and you'll be notified by <%= workshop.applications.notification %>. You only have to register and pay once you're accepted. We accept students based on the following:</p>
          <ul class="answer-list">
            <li>You must be a journalist or a student studying journalism</li>
            <li>You must have little or no coding experience</li>
            <li>We will give preference to applicants who will actively use these skills in the service of journalism</li>
          </ul>
        <p>Please read our <a href="faq.html">FAQs</a> before applying. <a href="mailto:team@codewithme.us">E-mail us</a> if you have any questions!</p>
        <iframe onLoad="window.scrollTo(0,650);" src="<%= workshop.applications.form %>" width="100%" height="2100" frameborder="0" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0">Loading...</iframe>

    </div>

    <%= partial( :sidebar, :locals => { :workshop => workshop, :show_apply => false }) %>

</div>